[lesson]   Solution: - **FIX_PLAN:**;  1. Installed `pillow`, `torchvision==0.27.1+cu130` (matching torch 2.12.1+cu130), `sentencepiece`.;  2. Built a local model mirror at `/root/.cache/apodex-1.0-2B-SFT-rebased_local` containing the original HF snapshot files + a copied `preprocessor_config.json` (sourced from the parent `Qwen/Qwen3.5-2B-Base` which has the same Qwen3VL config).;  3. Modified `phases/quantize_wrapper.sh` to auto-detect and prefer the local mirror when one exists at `/root/.cache/${MODEL_SHORT}_local`. The local-dir path makes auto_round's `mllm_load_model` take the `os.path.isdir()` branch (skipping the `list_repo_files` network call that fails in HF-offline mode) and makes `image_processing_auto` read the local file directly.;--;
